title: What Do You Do When You Screw Up?
itunes:title: What Do You Do When You Screw Up?
description:
Episode 474 - We all screw up, but what do you do when you screw up? Your response to your failures, flaws and screw ups are what will make you into the person you will become, so let's talk about it!
